&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You&amp;nbsp;will support a dedicated sales team end-to-end, acting as a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;steady, trusted partner in a high-volume environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;—prioritizing effectively, navigating competing demands, and&amp;nbsp;maintaining&amp;nbsp;focus on what matters most for our members and the business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
