&lt;p&gt;We are seeking&amp;nbsp;a driven and detail-oriented Senior&amp;nbsp;Accountant to join our growing finance team. This role is ideal for a self-starter with a strong&amp;nbsp;foundation in public accounting who is eager to apply their skills in a fast-paced, entrepreneurial&amp;nbsp;environment. You will play a key role in ensuring the accuracy and integrity of financial reporting and will have opportunities to contribute to process improvement,&amp;nbsp;technology adoption, and broader finance initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate is ambitious and eager to grow within a high-performing team. You are a&amp;nbsp;natural problem solver who takes ownership of your work and looks for ways to do things better.&amp;nbsp;You thrive in environments that reward initiative and aren’t afraid to raise your hand, ask&amp;nbsp;questions, or suggest a new approach. An interest in technology, especially how AI is reshaping&amp;nbsp;the accounting function, will set you apart. Equally important is how you show up for your team.&amp;nbsp;We’re looking for someone who is collaborative, approachable, and easy to work with, someone&amp;nbsp;who communicates openly, supports their colleagues, and contributes to a positive team culture.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
