&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Prepare journal entries, account reconciliations, and month-end/year-end close activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Assist in the preparation of financial statements and management reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Coordinate with external tax advisors on federal, state, and local tax matters; verify&amp;nbsp;timely payments, maintain organized tax records, and book related journal entries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams to ensure accurate coding and reporting of financial transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Identify and implement process improvements to enhance efficiency and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Leverage technology and AI-powered tools to streamline accounting workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Maintain and improve processes within Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Support external audits and liaise with auditors as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Assist the Senior Manager with ad hoc financial analysis and special projects&lt;/li&gt;
