&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;To support our growth, we’re seeking a dynamic&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Senior Corporate Counsel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Reporting to the&amp;nbsp;General Counsel,&amp;nbsp;you&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;will be a key member of the legal team, providing strategic legal guidance and transactional support across the organization. This role focuses on managing supplier and member agreements, advising on compliance matters, and supporting group&amp;nbsp;purchasing&amp;nbsp;operations in a highly regulated industry. You will partner with internal business leaders to ensure sound and strategic&amp;nbsp;advice&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;drive growth and operational excellence, while also managing relationships with external stakeholders.&amp;nbsp;Liaise&amp;nbsp;with outside counsel as needed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This position offers broad exposure across all lines of business and the opportunity to influence critical initiatives in a fast-growing, well-resourced company. Intellectual curiosity, strong business acumen, and&amp;nbsp;ability to communicate with internal and external stakeholders&amp;nbsp;(including supplier partners, private equity firms,&amp;nbsp;government agencies,&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;large enterprise organizations).&amp;nbsp;The ability to&amp;nbsp;anticipate&amp;nbsp;procurement trends and regulatory impacts&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;preferred.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
